[Template:Milestone 2](Template:Milestone_2 "wikilink") **Add-ons** are extensions for *SuperTux* which are distributed separately from the main distribution. In most cases, they are sets of levels contributed by users or groups of users. They may, however, include custom [tilesets](tileset "wikilink"), which may give these levels a very distinct look. Add-ons are a new feature of *version 0.3* and are *not* available in the [Milestone 1](Milestone_1 "wikilink") version.

Add-ons can be downloaded from within *SuperTux*. Simply ensure you have an internet connection, and select “Addons” from the main menu, where you can choose to install the currently available add-ons.

